Description: =============
        MinimalModbus
        =============
        
        There are several types of modbus protocols:
        
          * Modbus RTU
          * Modbus ??
        
        Typical usage::
        
         #!/usr/bin/env python
        
         import minimalmodbus
        
         instrument = minimalmodbus.Instrument(56) # Slave address
         temperature = instrument.read_register( 23541, 1 ) # Registernumber, number of decimals
        
        
        
        
